Error: New Error: "Internal Exception: Java.Io.IOException: An Existing Connection Was Forcibly Closed By The Remote Host."

Solution: Step 1: Check your internet connection: The error is commonly caused by a problem with your internet connection. Check your internet connection and try to reconnect to the game.

Step 2: Disable your Firewall: Your firewall might be blocking Minecraft from connecting to its servers. Disable your firewall temporarily and try to connect to the game.

